class=\"park-premium-title\">South Park Doggie Pawcademy</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>0</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens Monday at 8:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Gardena<!-- -->, <!-- -->CA</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge feature-badge\">PARKING</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">South Park Doggie Pawcademy is a premier dog school and theme park that offers an innovative, fun-filled environment where dogs can thrive. Located in a spacious, beautifully designed park, we provide a variety of services focused on socialization, physical fitness, and mental development. Our carefully crafted curriculum, led by experienced trainers, ensures that each dog receives personalized attention and a learning experience tailored to their needs. Whether your dog is working on obedience, agility, or socializing with new friends, our interactive classes and themed adventure zones make learning exciting. Plus, with seasonal Paw Social events, our park serves as a community hub where pet parents can connect, share tips, and enjoy the company of other dog lovers.\n\nWhat makes South Park Doggie Pawcademy truly unique is the combination of education and entertainment. Our state-of-the-art facilities feature dog-friendly play zones, challenging obstacle courses, and relaxation areas, ensuring dogs have plenty of space to explore, play, and unwind. We also offer premium staycare memberships for those looking for year-round accommodations, with discounts and perks for frequent visitors. Our goal is to provide a safe, enriching environment that supports both dogs&#x27; development and the bond between pet parents and their furry companions. Join us today and discover why we’re the ultimate destination for dogs and their families!</p></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->Gardena</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem\"><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in San Francisco, CA\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/san-francisco/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"padding:1rem\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:#0f172a\">San Francisco</h3><p style=\"font-size:0.875rem;color:#64748b\">50<!-- --> parks · <!-- -->4.6<!-- --> avg rating</p></div></a><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Los Angeles, CA\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/los-angeles/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"padding:1rem\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.125rem;font-w